Noor Ellis admitted a role in the murder of her husband Robert Kelvin Ellis in Bali last October . 
  Her body was found wrapped in plastic with his throat cut in a rice field . 
  She told a court she hired hitmen to kill her husband because he refused to give her money or a divorce . 
  Mrs Ellis faces the death penalty for premeditated murder . 
  Her husband was found with his wrists and feet bound in a ditch . 
  She was arrested along with her two maids and the boyfriend of one of the hitmen . 
  Mr Ellis was found dead at their home in October last year . 
  His wife said he died 'Because of the order from me'